                // Privacy Policy body paragraphs
                'Welcome to EASE, your trusted partner for seamless baggage storage and delivery in Kuching. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled securely. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our website and services.' => '欢迎使用 EASE，您在古晋无缝行李寄存与配送服务的可信赖合作伙伴。我们致力于保护您的隐私，确保您的个人信息得到安全处理。本隐私政策说明我们在您使用网站和服务时如何收集、使用、披露及保护您的信息。',
                'We collect various types of information to provide and improve our services:' => '我们收集多种类型的信息以提供和改善我们的服务：',
                'When you use our services, you may provide us with personal details such as your name, contact information, and payment details.' => '当您使用我们的服务时，您可能会向我们提供个人详细信息，例如您的姓名、联系方式和付款详情。',
                'We collect information about how you interact with our website, including your IP address, browser type, and browsing activity.' => '我们收集有关您如何与我们网站互动的信息，包括您的 IP 地址、浏览器类型和浏览活动。',
                'We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience on our website. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.' => '我们使用 Cookie 和类似技术来提升您在网站上的体验。您可以通过浏览器设置管理您的 Cookie 偏好。',
                'We use your information for the following purposes:' => '我们将您的信息用于以下目的：',
                'To process and manage your baggage storage and delivery requests.' => '处理和管理您的行李寄存及配送请求。',
                'To analyze usage trends and improve the functionality of our site.' => '分析使用趋势并改善网站功能。',
                'To send updates, confirmations, and promotional materials related to our services.' => '发送与我们服务相关的更新、确认信息及推广材料。',
                'To detect, prevent, and address fraudulent activities and other security issues.' => '检测、预防和处理欺诈活动及其他安全问题。',
                'We may share your information in the following circumstances:' => '在以下情况下，我们可能会共享您的信息：',
                'We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in delivering our services, such as payment processors and IT support.' => '我们可能会与协助我们提供服务的第三方服务提供商共享您的信息，例如付款处理商和 IT 支持。',
                'We may disclose your information if required by law or to respond to legal processes or requests.' => '如法律要求或为回应法律程序或请求，我们可能会披露您的信息。',
                'In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, your information may be transferred as part of the transaction.' => '在合并、收购或资产出售的情况下，您的信息可能作为交易的一部分进行转移。',
                'We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.' => '我们采用行业标准安全措施，保护您的个人信息免遭未经授权的访问、使用或披露。但请注意，互联网传输或电子存储均无法做到完全安全。',
                'You have the following rights regarding your personal information:' => '您对个人信息享有以下权利：',
                'You can request access to and correction of your personal information.' => '您可以请求访问和更正您的个人信息。',
