                'Select date and time you will drop off your luggage.' => '请选择您托运行李的日期和时间。',
                'Select date and time you will collect up your luggage.' => '请选择您领取行李的日期和时间。',
                'The selected time must be between 07:00 and 19:00.' => '所选时间必须在 07:00 至 19:00 之间。',
                'Drop-off date and time cannot be in the past.' => '送货日期和时间不能是过去的时间。',
                'Pick-up date and time cannot be in the past.' => '取货日期和时间不能是过去的日期和时间。',
                'Please select a time that is at least 2 hours from current time which is' => '请选择一个与当前时间至少相隔 2 小时的时间',
                'Time:' => '时间：',
                'Select where you would like to store your luggage.' => '请选择您希望存放行李的位置。',
                'Select the number of bags you want to store.' => '请选择您要存放的袋子数量。',
                'Select date and time you will collect your luggage.' => '请选择您领取行李的日期和时间。',
                // TnC headings
                'Acceptance of Terms and Conditions of' => '接受以下机构的条款与条件：',
                'Liabilities of' => '以下机构的责任：',
                'EASE Storage Hub (Malaysia):' => 'EASE 寄存中心（马来西亚）：',
                'To ensure eligibility for coverage, customers must:' => '为确保符合保障资格，客户必须：',
                'In the event of damage, loss, or theft:' => '如发生损坏、丢失或盗窃：',
                // TnC Definition of Luggage
                'is defined by airline regulations and can be checked or carried on the customer\'s intended flight. Each piece of standard luggage must not exceed a total of 180 cm in dimensions and must weigh no more than 23kg. Items such as sports equipment (including but not limited to surfboards, snowboards, golf bags, and bicycles), musical instruments (such as cellos, guitars, pianos, and drums), and baby strollers/carriages are NOT considered standard luggage.' => '根据航空公司规定，可作为托运或随身行李携带上旅客预定的航班。每件标准行李总尺寸不得超过180厘米，重量不得超过23公斤。运动器材（包括但不限于冲浪板、滑雪板、高尔夫球袋及自行车）、乐器（如大提琴、吉他、钢琴及鼓）及婴儿车均不属于标准行李。',
                'Any luggage or items that do not meet these specifications are categorized as' => '任何不符合上述规格的行李或物品均归类为',
                '. All luggage must be in good condition and securely closed, sealed, or zipped.' => '。所有行李必须状况良好，并妥善关闭、密封或拉好拉链。',
                'Each piece of luggage must be kept separate and not bundled or attached to any other items, including but not limited to plastic bags, travel pillows, or smaller bags.' => '每件行李必须单独存放，不得与其他物品捆绑或连接，包括但不限于塑料袋、旅行枕或小型手提袋。',
                'Luggage MUST NOT contain any illegal, dangerous, prohibited, risky, or suspicious items.' => '行李中绝对不得装有任何非法、危险、违禁、危险或可疑物品。',
                'reserves the right to refuse any luggage or belongings that are deemed unacceptable.' => '保留拒绝任何被认为不可接受的行李或物品的权利。',
                'Attachments like name tags, accessory dolls, pillows, or small bags that are not counted as a single piece of luggage are NOT guaranteed in terms of their condition or risk of loss.' => '名牌、装饰玩偶、枕头或小型手提袋等不计为单件行李的附件，其状况及丢失风险概不保证。',
                // TnC Booking Conditions
                'Orders must be submitted prior to service usage and confirmed by' => '订单须在使用服务前提交，并由',
                'reserves the right to deny or cancel bookings if there is a suspicion of misuse of our services by you or a third party for commercial purposes.' => '有权拒绝或取消预订，如发现您或第三方存在将我们服务用于商业目的之嫌疑。',
                'Customers are responsible for ensuring that all provided information and contact details are accurate and accessible.' => '客户有责任确保所提供的所有信息和联系方式准确无误。',
                'A booking is considered confirmed ONLY after payment is successfully completed and the customer has received a confirmation email from easesarawak@gmail.com' => '预订仅在付款成功完成且客户收到来自 easesarawak@gmail.com 的确认邮件后方视为已确认',
                // TnC Amendment Conditions
                'To modify a booking, requests must be submitted via email or live chat at least 3 hours before the service is used.' => '如需修改预订，须于使用服务至少3小时前通过电子邮件或在线客服提交申请。',
                'Once the amendment is confirmed, the customer will receive an updated email from' => '一旦修改获得确认，客户将收到来自',
                // TnC Cancellation
                'To cancel an order and receive a full refund, requests must be submitted via email at least 2 hours before the service is used.' => '如需取消订单并获得全额退款，须于使用服务至少2小时前通过电子邮件提交申请。',
                'Bookings or orders that are canceled after the service has started or 1 hour before the service start time WILL NOT qualify for a refund.' => '在服务开始后或服务开始前1小时内取消的预订或订单将不予退款。',
                'Refunds will be processed within 7-14 business days.' => '退款将在7至14个工作日内处理。',
                'Refunds will ONLY be issued through our accepted wireless transfer Methods.' => '退款仅通过我们接受的无线转账方式发放。',
                'The booking/order will be regarded as a "NO SHOW" starting from the scheduled service time.' => '从预定服务时间起，该预订/订单将被视为"未到场"。',
                // TnC Notification of Change
                'Any updates or notifications regarding changes to an order or booking will ONLY be sent from' => '任何关于订单或预订变更的更新或通知将仅从',
                'After service amendments or changes, customers should keep the confirmation email for reference.' => '服务修改或变更后，客户应保留确认邮件以供参考。',
                'In the case of service cancellations, customers should also retain the confirmation email for reference.' => '如遇服务取消，客户也应保留确认邮件以供参考。',
                'retains the right to update these terms and conditions periodically in accordance with the Standard Terms and Conditions.' => '保留定期依据标准条款与条件更新本条款与条件的权利。',
                // TnC In-Town Delivery
                'Order(s) and customer booking(s) are confirmed ONLY AFTER the payment has been successfully processed by the customer.' => '订单及客户预订仅在客户成功完成付款后方视为已确认。',
                'Scheduled deliveries will be made according to the established timetable and cannot be set for a specific time.' => '预定配送将按既定时刻表进行，不能指定特定时间。',
                'couriers, drivers, or staff will collect luggage from the designated location 15 minutes BEFORE or AFTER the scheduled drop-off time at the gate or lobby of the property for outbound deliveries. Please ensure that the luggage is ready for drop-off 15 minutes before the scheduled time.' => '快递员、司机或员工将于预定交付时间前后15分钟内，在物业门口或大堂取件（出站配送）。请确保行李在预定时间前15分钟已准备好交付。',
                'For hotel drop-off and pick-up, the hotel concierge facility is only available to the hotel guests. Customers should provide their check-in and check-out details or confirmation for us to coordinate with the hotel for luggage transfer. Non-hotel guest customers must make their luggage available at the designated location as per the scheduled time.' => '酒店送取行李时，礼宾服务仅限酒店住客使用。客户需提供入住及退房信息或确认函，以便我们与酒店协调行李转运。非酒店住客须按预定时间在指定地点提供行李。',
                'The in-town delivery service is ONLY available in' => '市区配送服务仅在',
                'and does not include any special areas.' => '提供，不包含特殊区域。',
                'If the customer is late in placing their luggage at the delivery location, including but not limited to airports, hotels, shopping malls, or homes, our courier will ONLY wait for up to 15 minutes.' => '如客户未能及时将行李放置在配送地点（包括但不限于机场、酒店、购物中心或住所），我们的快递员最多等待15分钟。',
                'If the customer is not available 15 minutes after the scheduled time or if we are unable to contact the customer, the order will be classified as a "No Show" and will be canceled WITHOUT a refund.' => '若预定时间15分钟后客户仍未到场，或我们无法联系到客户，该订单将被列为"未到场"并予以取消，不予退款。',
                'couriers, drivers, or staff cannot locate the luggage at the designated location, they will contact the customer exclusively via phone or email.' => '快递员、司机或员工无法在指定地点找到行李时，将仅通过电话或电子邮件联系客户。',
                'SHALL NOT be liable for any FRAGILE, PERISHABLE, ILLEGAL, or PROHIBITED item(s) or content(s) of luggage delivered.' => '对所配送行李中任何易碎、易腐烂、非法或违禁物品及内容物概不负责。',
                'In-Town Delivery Service operates daily from 07:00 to 21:00.' => '市区配送服务每日07:00至21:00运营。',
                // TnC Luggage Storage
                'The storage duration begins at the scheduled reservation time even if the luggage is dropped off after the appointed time.' => '寄存期限从预定时间开始计算，即使行李在预定时间之后才交付。',
                'If the luggage is dropped off before the scheduled time, the storage duration will start from when the luggage is actually dropped off.' => '如行李在预定时间前交付，寄存期限将从实际交付时间开始计算。',
                'If the luggage is retrieved after the scheduled retrieval time, additional service fees will be applied.' => '如行李在预定取件时间后才取回，将收取额外服务费用。',
                'If the luggage is retrieved before the scheduled retrieval time, no refund will be provided.' => '如行李在预定取件时间前取回，不予退款。',
                'Customers may ONLY STORE luggage or belongings DURING SERVICE HOURS in accordance with the regulations of EASE STORAGE SDN. BHD..' => '客户仅可在营业时间内按 EASE STORAGE SDN. BHD. 规定寄存行李或物品。',
                'To extend the storage duration, customers should contact us via website live chat or email and receive confirmation ONLY from EASE STORAGE SDN. BHD. via email at' => '如需延长寄存期限，客户应通过网站在线客服或电子邮件联系我们，并仅接受来自 EASE STORAGE SDN. BHD. 的电子邮件确认，邮箱为',
                'We will confirm the extension of storage duration ONLY after a new Estimated Time Pick-up (ETP) is set AND the service fee for both the previous and new ETP is paid.' => '仅在设置新的预计取件时间（ETP）并支付原ETP及新ETP的服务费后，我们方可确认延长寄存期限。',
                'Luggage not picked up within 30 days after the ETP, without an extension for storage duration, will be considered abandoned property and disposed of.' => '在ETP后30天内未取回且未申请延长寄存的行李，将被视为无主财产予以处置。',
                'If a customer wishes to pick up any belongings from their luggage during storage, they MUST retrieve all items AND close the order. We DO NOT accept partial retrieval requests.' => '如客户希望在寄存期间取出行李中的物品，必须取回全部物品并关闭订单。我们不接受部分取件申请。',
                'We WILL NOT open customer luggage or remove any items from the luggage under any circumstances or upon customer request, EXCEPT in cooperation with official or governmental authorities during lawful investigations.' => '除配合官方或政府机构进行合法调查外，我们在任何情况下均不会打开客户行李或取出其中任何物品。',
                'SHALL NOT be liable for any FRAGILE, PERISHABLE, ILLEGAL, or PROHIBITED item(s) or content(s) of luggage stored at our facility.' => '对寄存于本设施的行李中任何易碎、易腐烂、非法或违禁物品及内容物概不负责。',
                'Storage Service operates daily from 07:00 to 21:00.' => '寄存服务每日07:00至21:00运营。',
                // TnC Depositing/Retrieving
                'The customer MUST provide valid references, including a passport, Malaysian ID, or driver\'s license, along with the order confirmation or email, to verify the consignee\'s identity. Copies or photos of ID cards or passports will NOT be accepted.' => '客户必须提供有效证件（包括护照、马来西亚身份证或驾驶执照）及订单确认函或电子邮件，以核实收件人身份。不接受身份证或护照的复印件或照片。',
                'If the customer does not have valid or correct order references,' => '如客户未持有有效或正确的订单凭证，',
                'reserves the right to deny the retrieval request.' => '保留拒绝取件申请的权利。',
                'does NOT accept any partial deposit/retrieval requests or allow the pickup of personal items from luggage during the storage period.' => '不接受任何部分存取申请，也不允许在寄存期间取出行李中的个人物品。',
                'Customers may ONLY retrieve luggage or belongings during service hours in accordance with the regulations of' => '客户仅可在营业时间内，依照以下机构的规定领取行李或物品：',
                'If stored belongings are to be retrieved by another individual or third party, the customer must provide the valid Malaysian ID or passport of the authorized consignee via website live chat or email. This information will be required for identity verification when the authorized consignee retrieves the belongings.' => '如寄存物品需由他人或第三方取回，客户须通过网站在线客服或电子邮件提供授权取件人的有效马来西亚身份证或护照。授权取件人取件时需凭此信息进行身份核实。',
                // TnC Acceptance of Terms
                'Please thoroughly review these terms and conditions before accessing and using our services. By using our services, you are agreeing to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree to these terms, you must CANCEL and refrain from accessing or using our services. In cases where your booking or service usage is handled by a third party on your behalf, it is implied that you accept these terms and our Privacy Policy.' => '在访问和使用我们的服务之前，请仔细阅读本条款与条件。使用我们的服务即表示您同意受本条款约束。如您不同意本条款，您必须取消并停止访问或使用我们的服务。若您的预订或服务使用由第三方代为处理，则视为您接受本条款及我们的隐私政策。',
                'Our services are only available to individuals aged 18 or older who are considered legal adults under Malaysian law. By using our website, application, or services, you confirm that you are 18 years of age or older, agree to abide by these terms and policies, and are capable of entering into a contract with' => '我们的服务仅面向根据马来西亚法律被视为法定成年人（18周岁及以上）的人士。使用我们的网站、应用程序或服务，即表示您确认您已年满18周岁，同意遵守本条款及政策，并具备与',
                // TnC Company Information
                '(1589189-T) is a registered entity in Malaysia, with its registered office located at First Floor, Unit No E297, Lot 11382 or Old Lot No 11099, Block E, Section 64, ICOM SQUARE, Jalan Pending, 93450 Kuching, Sarawak.' => '（1589189-T）是在马来西亚注册的实体，其注册办事处位于砂拉越古晋市93450 Jalan Pending，ICOM SQUARE，E座，第64段，Lot 11382（旧地号11099），E297单位，一楼。',
                // TnC Pricing
                'All prices, payments, and financial transactions are to be conducted exclusively via our website or at our storage hub. Any financial or transactional request that is made outside these official channels IS NOT authorized by us.' => '所有价格、付款及财务交易须独家通过我们的网站或寄存中心进行。在这些官方渠道以外发起的任何财务或交易请求均未经我们授权。',
                'Service prices are listed on our official platforms, and while prices may change, the amount will be FIXED once a booking or reservation is confirmed. All listed prices include 6% SST. Any requests not included in the initial transaction will be treated as a separate order and may be subject to different pricing. Payments can be made by credit card, debit card, or cash in' => '服务价格在我们的官方平台上列出，价格虽可能调整，但一旦预订或预约确认，金额将固定不变。所有标注价格均含6% SST。初始交易以外的任何额外请求将视为单独订单，可能适用不同定价。付款可使用信用卡、借记卡或现金（',
                '. Accepted payment methods are listed below:' => '）进行。接受的付款方式如下：',
                // TnC Receipts
                'Once payment is confirmed, all service pricing details will appear on your invoice, and no hidden charges will apply. You have the right to request clarification if anything in the invoice is unclear. The individual using the service must be the same person collecting the luggage. The amounts listed on the invoice and receipt will match exactly, and the receipt is provided once the transaction is complete, signaling agreement to these terms. By accepting the receipt, you acknowledge that the service has concluded.' => '付款确认后，所有服务定价详情将显示在您的发票上，不收取任何隐性费用。如发票中有任何不清晰之处，您有权要求说明。使用服务的人必须与取回行李的人为同一人。发票与收据上的金额完全一致，收据在交易完成后提供，代表您同意本条款。接受收据即表示您确认服务已完成。',
                // TnC Responsibilities
                'We commit to delivering services as described on our website or at our store. If we fail to complete an inbound delivery within the specified timeframe, you will be entitled to a 100% refund. If we fail to meet the scheduled time for an outbound delivery, we will cover the necessary costs to ensure your luggage reaches your final specified destination. Any changes in circumstances that could affect your service will be communicated to you using the contact details you have provided.' => '我们承诺按网站或门店所述提供服务。如我们未能在规定时间内完成入站配送，您将获得100%退款。如我们未能按时完成出站配送，我们将承担必要费用以确保您的行李送达最终指定目的地。任何可能影响您服务的情况变化，将通过您提供的联系方式告知您。',
                // TnC User Responsibilities
                'You confirm that no FRAGILE, PERISHABLE, ILLEGAL or PROHIBITED item(s) or content(s) are included in the luggage being delivered or stored, and that the services are used correctly. You are responsible for any loss or damage resulting from misuse or violation of these terms. Retain your invoice or certification for verification purposes during check-out. You confirm that all information you provide is accurate, whether given by you or a third party on your behalf. Our staff may request proof of identification, such as a credit card, driving licence or passport, to verify your identity.' => '您确认所配送或寄存的行李中不含任何易碎、易腐烂、非法或违禁物品，且服务使用方式正确。因滥用或违反本条款造成的任何损失或损坏，您须承担责任。请保留发票或凭证，以便退房时核实。您确认所提供的所有信息均准确无误，无论是您本人还是代理方提供的。我们的员工可能要求您出示身份证明（如信用卡、驾驶执照或护照）以核实身份。',
                // TnC Delivery Policy
                'Our services must be used for lawful purposes. By utilizing our delivery service, you agree to our terms and comply with Malaysian law. We will not tamper with your luggage, but in certain circumstances, we may cooperate with Malaysian government officials for investigations or to prevent illegal activities. If any suspicious or prohibited items are discovered, either by official notice or through screening methods like X-rays, we may ask you to allow our staff to inspect your luggage. Refusing such inspection may result in the cancellation of your service without a refund for security reasons. We reserve the right to decline or cancel any booking, reservation, or service if terms are violated or if illegal activity is suspected.' => '我们的服务必须用于合法目的。使用我们的配送服务，即表示您同意我们的条款并遵守马来西亚法律。我们不会擅自打开您的行李，但在某些情况下，我们可能配合马来西亚政府官员进行调查或防止非法活动。如通过官方通知或X光等筛查方式发现任何可疑或违禁物品，我们可能要求您允许员工检查行李。拒绝接受检查可能导致服务被取消且不予退款。如违反条款或涉嫌违法活动，我们保留拒绝或取消任何预订、预约或服务的权利。',
                'A Standard Luggage is defined as luggage where the combined dimensions (Width, Length, and Height) do not exceed 180 cm, and the weight does not exceed 23kg.' => '标准行李定义为总尺寸（宽+长+高）不超过180厘米且重量不超过23公斤的行李。',
                'A Special Luggage is defined as luggage that does not fall within the Standard Luggage category and will be charged based on a custom quote and will be subject to storage availability.' => '特殊行李定义为不符合标准行李类别的行李，将根据定制报价收费，并视存储容量而定。',
                // TnC Events Beyond Control
                'We are not liable for any failure to provide services or protect your luggage due to circumstances outside our control, including but not limited to:' => '因超出我们控制范围的情况导致无法提供服务或保护您的行李，我们概不负责，包括但不限于：',
                'Failure to comply with aviation security.' => '未能遵守航空安全规定。',
                'Inability to deliver luggage to the airport or hotel on time by third parties.' => '第三方未能及时将行李送达机场或酒店。',
                'Late bookings, reservations, or cancellations.' => '预订、预约或取消迟误。',
                'Actions of government or safety authorities (e.g., police, customs, airport operators).' => '政府或安全机构的行动（如警察、海关、机场运营商）。',
                'Disruptions in regional or national transportation.' => '地区或全国交通中断。',
                'Natural disasters (e.g., floods, earthquakes, tsunamis).' => '自然灾害（如洪水、地震、海啸）。',
                'Situations caused by third-party actions beyond our control (e.g., riots, strikes, fires, investigations).' => '因超出我们控制范围的第三方行为引起的情况（如暴乱、罢工、火灾、调查）。',
                // TnC Prohibited Items
                'For the safety and security of our clients and their belongings, we enforce strict guidelines on items that cannot be stored or delivered through our service. Below is a list of items that are prohibited for storage or transport with EASE STORAGE SDN. BHD.:' => '为保障客户及其物品的安全，我们对不得通过本服务存放或配送的物品实施严格规定。以下为 EASE STORAGE SDN. BHD. 禁止存放或运输的物品清单：',
                'Living or deceased plants or animals.' => '活体或已死亡的植物或动物。',
                'Currency (banknotes, coins, credit/debit cards, and travelers cheques).' => '货币（钞票、硬币、信用卡/借记卡及旅行支票）。',
                'Fine art, antiques, jewelry, important documents, software, or any other irreplaceable valuables.' => '艺术品、古董、珠宝、重要文件、软件或任何其他无法替代的贵重物品。',
                'Materials deemed pornographic or indecent.' => '被视为色情或不雅的材料。',
                'Precious metals (such as gold or silver in any form) and gemstones.' => '贵金属（如任何形式的金或银）及宝石。',
                'Explosives, fuel, hazardous, or flammable materials.' => '爆炸物、燃料、危险品或易燃材料。',
                'Radioactive substances or items that emit strong odors or fumes.' => '放射性物质或散发强烈气味或烟雾的物品。',
                'Firearms, ammunition, illegal drugs, or any other substances controlled by local law.' => '枪支、弹药、非法药物或任何受当地法律管制的物质。',
                'Items considered risky, dangerous, or harmful as defined by civil aviation authorities.' => '民航当局认定的危险、有害或高风险物品。',
                'Stolen goods or contraband.' => '赃物或走私品。',
                'Perishable or spoiled food that may emit fumes, generate liquids, or strong odors.' => '可能散发烟雾、产生液体或强烈气味的易腐烂或变质食物。',
                'Batteries and electronic devices (including watches, clocks, phones, laptops, or tablets containing batteries).' => '电池及电子设备（包括含有电池的手表、时钟、手机、笔记本电脑或平板电脑）。',
                'Waste or refuse.' => '废物或垃圾。',
                // TnC Liabilities
                'For confirmed orders, we ensure that the delivery or service will be completed on time and directed to the correct destination and recipient. We shall not be held liable for any loss or damage resulting from FRAGILE, PERISHABLE, ILLEGAL or PROHIBITED item(s) or content(s).' => '对于已确认订单，我们确保配送或服务将按时完成并送达正确目的地和收件人。对于易碎、易腐烂、非法或违禁物品及内容物造成的任何损失或损坏，我们概不负责。',
                // TnC Insurance
                'At' => '在',
                ', the safety and security of your belongings are our top priority. All luggage stored, transferred, or delivered with us is automatically covered by our standard insurance policy in the event of damage, theft, or complete loss of luggage caused by mishandling on our part. For added peace of mind, customers may choose to purchase additional insurance coverage.' => '，您物品的安全是我们的首要任务。所有通过我们寄存、转运或配送的行李，在因我方操作失误导致损坏、被盗或完全丢失时，自动享有我们的标准保险保障。为进一步安心，客户可选择购买额外保险。',
                'For Standard Insurance, compensation is limited to the actual market value of the contents, up to RM1,000 per order.' => '标准保险的赔偿金额以内容物实际市场价值为限，每笔订单最高赔偿RM1,000。',
                'For Extra Coverage, compensation is limited to the actual market value of the contents, up to RM2,500 per order.' => '额外保障的赔偿金额以内容物实际市场价值为限，每笔订单最高赔偿RM2,500。',
                'Accessories such as luggage tags, padlocks, small bags, luggage covers, and decorative items are excluded from this insurance.' => '行李牌、挂锁、小型手提袋、行李套及装饰品等配件不在本保险保障范围内。',
                'Lost individual items within a bag are not covered unless the entire luggage is lost or stolen.' => '除非整件行李丢失或被盗，否则行李内单件物品的丢失不在保障范围内。',
                'Wear and tear such as scratches, scuff marks, or other minimal damage caused by normal handling is not covered.' => '正常处理造成的磨损，如划痕、磨损痕迹或其他轻微损坏，不在保障范围内。',
                'Ensure all luggage is in good condition, securely closed, zipped, and sealed before handover.' => '交付前确保所有行李状况良好、妥善关闭、拉好拉链并密封。',
                'No FRAGILE, PERISHABLE, ILLEGAL, or PROHIBITED item(s) or content(s) are included in the luggage being delivered or stored.' => '所配送或寄存的行李中不含任何易碎、易腐烂、非法或违禁物品。',
                'Claims must be submitted in writing within 24 hours of the completion of the service.' => '索赔须于服务完成后24小时内以书面形式提交。',
                'A police report or incident documentation may be required for claims above RM1,000.' => '超过RM1,000的索赔可能需要提供警方报告或事件证明文件。',
                'Our team will assess and respond to claims within 7-14 business days.' => '我们的团队将在7至14个工作日内评估并回复索赔。',
                // TnC Customer Rights
                'You have the right to modify or cancel your booking or reservation up to 2 hours before the scheduled time for luggage storage and delivery service.' => '您有权在行李寄存和配送服务预定时间前2小时内修改或取消预订。',
                // TnC Payment
                'Ringgit Malaysia (RM)' => '马来西亚令吉（RM）',
                'You will receive a receipt (digital or printed) upon completion of payment.' => '付款完成后，您将收到一张收据（电子版或纸质版）。',
                'Credit/Debit Card (VISA, MasterCard)' => '信用卡/借记卡（VISA、MasterCard）',

                'Information' => '信息',
                'IN-TOWN DELIVERY' => '市区配送',
                'LUGGAGE STORAGE' => '行李寄存',
            ],
        ];
    }
}

